snippet.textDisplay:
We are not together anymore but Whenever i listen to this song i remember one dearest friend of mine.. she was like the colours to my sky and all the bright stars twinkling on dark nights .. her presence made me feel complete, i felt it in the deepest of my heart and soul, igniting all my senses of being alive.. in short she was everything to me...but unfortunately, I had to make tuffest decision of my life, I had to let go of my dreams with her. As God has some other plans for us.. and that plan was anything but not us being together ...  But deep down I'm grateful for those days, moments, warm hugs that used to calm my heartbeat with the feelings of togetherness where u and me become us, like life's getting its eternal reason for happiness. i will always glorify them within myself as those were real and it happened. And that was the time where I asked God for nothing but her presence with me.. as it was all the happiness and peace in the world for me ..❤❤ and only thing I craved as much as I craved her was her happiness, that beautiful smile and real laughter which made us forget about rest of world..

But now as we are not together, and as i  listen to this song I feel this lines for her !

Yaad hai muze Teri har aada.
Muskurahate Teri ...

Meri ye dua hai ke Tera jewan uhi....
chalta rahe , sari khwahishe ho puri.. 
Teri duniya me na ho kabhi meri Kami... ❤ 🫂
